### REST Client API Testing File
### Use VS Code "REST Client" extension to test these endpoints directly

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api

### ====================
### SERVICES
### ====================

### Get all services
GET {{baseUrl}}/services
Accept: application/json

### ====================
### TESTIMONIALS
### ====================

### Get all testimonials
GET {{baseUrl}}/testimonials
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a new testimonial
POST {{baseUrl}}/testimonials
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "David Ochieng",
    "message": "Excellent service and very professional staff.",
    "rating": 5
}

### ====================
### PATIENTS
### ====================

### Get all patients
GET {{baseUrl}}/patients
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a new patient
POST {{baseUrl}}/patients
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Jane Doe",
    "email": "jane.doe@example.com",
    "phone": "+254712345678"
}

### ====================
### APPOINTMENTS
### ====================

### Get all appointments
GET {{baseUrl}}/appointments
Accept: application/json

###

### Book an appointment (with new patient details)
POST {{baseUrl}}/appointments
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "John Smith",
    "email": "john.smith@example.com",
    "phone": "+254789012345",
    "service": "Cardiology",
    "date": "2026-05-10",
    "time": "14:30"
}

###

### Update appointment status (Replace ID with actual ID)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/appointments/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "status": "confirmed"
}

###

### Delete appointment (Replace ID with actual ID)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/appointments/1

### ====================
### CONTACT INQUIRIES
### ====================

### Submit a contact message
POST {{baseUrl}}/contact
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Alice Wonderland",
    "email": "alice@example.com",
    "message": "I would like to know more about your pediatric services."
}
